<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="code-of-conduct"><a class="anchor" href="#code-of-conduct"></a>Code of Conduct</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The core Asciidoctor project is governed by the <a href="https://github.com/asciidoctor/.github/blob/HEAD/CODE-OF-CONDUCT.md">Code of Conduct</a> for the Asciidoctor community of projects.
By participating, you&#8217;re agreeing to honor this code.
Let&#8217;s work together to make this a welcoming, professional, inclusive, and safe environment for everyone.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="versioning-and-release-policy"><a class="anchor" href="#versioning-and-release-policy"></a>Versioning and Release Policy</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This project adheres to semantic versioning (<strong>major.minor.patch</strong>).
Typically, patch releases are only made for the current minor release.
However, exceptions are made on a case-by-case basis to address security vulnerabilities and other high-priority issues.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
